Proud to join colleagues of the @HBCUCaucus, @HispanicCaucus & @CAPAC in requesting the inclusion of the #FUTUREAct in the upcoming government funding package. 

We relied on the Senate and they failed. 

@HouseDemocrats can still get the job done. https://adams.house.gov/media-center/press-releases/adams-calls-leadership-support-future-act …

When people are sick, they shouldn’t have to choose between providing for their families or buying prescription medications. 

#BigPharma has taken advantage of the American people, overcharging and over-profiting. 

@HouseDemocrats are fighting back with #HR3.
